-----------------------------------------------------------------------	
	JS Auto Validate
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

The objetive is easy, create the validation of html with javascript
many simple and fast for all levels of development

Actualy the file "default.js" have two types to validate :

	Not Null and E-mail 
	
	
Using "default.js" in your project, add the type of validation for the
<input type="text" in property ACCEPT.


Properties of tags INPUT :

	ACCEPT receive the type of validation
	
	TITLE receive the name for input


DIV to show messages errors :

	<div id="Errors"></div>


Exemple :

	- This input is required NotNull and Email
		<input type="text" name="username" title="Username"	accept="notnull,email" />
	
	- This input is required only Email
		<input type="text" name="email" title="Username"	accept="email" />
	
	- This input is required only NotNull
		<input type="text" name="username" title="Username"	accept="notnull" />
	
	